title: Eagles, Jerry Jones, OBJ, Aaron Rodgers, & Teddy Bridgewater
itunes:title: Eagles, Jerry Jones, OBJ, Aaron Rodgers, & Teddy Bridgewater
description:
Colin discusses why Philadelphia Eagles S Malcolm Jenkins is his new favorite player, the influence Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones has over the NFL, why New York Giants WR Odell Beckham Jr. is different from other players, Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers' new contract, and the New York Jets trading Teddy Bridgewater to the New Orleans Saints. Guests include Nick Wright, Rob Parker, and James Harrison.
